  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ursid</strong> is a zen puzzle game inspired by the constellations and the beauty of their imaginary pictures. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the role of the little boy Aster, players will <strong>freely explore</strong> the star sky, <strong>connect</strong> the stars, <strong>find out</strong> the hidden images, and gradually reveal an emotional <strong>father-son story</strong> while counting down to the moment <strong>the Ursid Shower</strong> appears.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925290/extras/75b1c8970f7f08f5774872ad888a7773.poster.avif?t=1772699519\" width=800 height=800 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925290/extras/75b1c8970f7f08f5774872ad888a7773.webm?t=1772699519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925290/extras/75b1c8970f7f08f5774872ad888a7773.mp4?t=1772699519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A total of 40+ handcrafted detailed levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Non-linear level solving progression. Players can freely choose the levels they want to solve, which follows the main story.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925290/extras/fd229e34fed8cb6c515e6517354741f2.poster.avif?t=1772699519\" width=800 height=412 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925290/extras/fd229e34fed8cb6c515e6517354741f2.webm?t=1772699519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925290/extras/fd229e34fed8cb6c515e6517354741f2.mp4?t=1772699519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Familiar connecting dots mechanics, which is refreshed by adding the challenge of hint numbers. Sometimes to find out a constellation needs a little bit of imagination!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cozy and meditative atmosphere with a heartwarming story about father-son relationship.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925290/extras/26c1c646541e2703a35a6cf49104da4b.poster.avif?t=1772699519\" width=600 height=486 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925290/extras/26c1c646541e2703a35a6cf49104da4b.webm?t=1772699519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925290/extras/26c1c646541e2703a35a6cf49104da4b.mp4?t=1772699519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ursid</strong> is a zen puzzle game inspired by the constellations and the beauty of their imaginary pictures. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the role of the little boy Aster, players will <strong>freely explore</strong> the star sky, <strong>connect</strong> the stars, <strong>find out</strong> the hidden images, and gradually reveal an emotional <strong>father-son story</strong> while counting down to the moment <strong>the Ursid Shower</strong> appears.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925290/extras/75b1c8970f7f08f5774872ad888a7773.poster.avif?t=1772699519\" width=800 height=800 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925290/extras/75b1c8970f7f08f5774872ad888a7773.webm?t=1772699519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925290/extras/75b1c8970f7f08f5774872ad888a7773.mp4?t=1772699519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A total of 40+ handcrafted detailed levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Non-linear level solving progression. Players can freely choose the levels they want to solve, which follows the main story.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925290/extras/fd229e34fed8cb6c515e6517354741f2.poster.avif?t=1772699519\" width=800 height=412 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925290/extras/fd229e34fed8cb6c515e6517354741f2.webm?t=1772699519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925290/extras/fd229e34fed8cb6c515e6517354741f2.mp4?t=1772699519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Familiar connecting dots mechanics, which is refreshed by adding the challenge of hint numbers. Sometimes to find out a constellation needs a little bit of imagination!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cozy and meditative atmosphere with a heartwarming story about father-son relationship.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925290/extras/26c1c646541e2703a35a6cf49104da4b.poster.avif?t=1772699519\" width=600 height=486 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925290/extras/26c1c646541e2703a35a6cf49104da4b.webm?t=1772699519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925290/extras/26c1c646541e2703a35a6cf49104da4b.mp4?t=1772699519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
